{"tid":2439098,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁國雄就立會搶文件案　終院批上訴許可","createTime":"2021-03-09T03:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T04:33:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0b31173f22e58d1e58e9c41b58a1291416eed5","tid":2439098,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】梁國雄立法會搶文件案，他就立法會特權法能否用於控告議員，獲終審法院申請上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n因民主派初選案正還柙的梁國雄，由囚車送到終審法院聆訊。他的太太陳寶瑩、社民連主席黃浩銘等到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄在2016年擔任立法會議員時，在委員會會議上搶去時任發展局副局長馬紹祥桌上文件，被控違反立法會特權法的藐視罪，原審裁判官裁定特權法不適用於控告議員，之後律政司在高院上訴庭上訴得直，案件發還裁判法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄就案件向終院申請上訴許可獲批。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426693&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy4vgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=d3c37dd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426693&h=77e92747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426693</a>"},{"pid":"4494ceba42dad51b20457ce25e8203d8c520df9b","tid":2439098,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014972813bfb919d114c5d0f30e5308a29cd08c9","tid":2439098,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}